      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber">823.303-70</ph> Contract clause.</title>
      <conbody>
         <p xtrc="P">Contracting officers shall insert clause <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref "
                  base="Section_852_223_71_T48_50216422135"
                  href="Section_852_223_71_T48_50216422135.dita#Section_852_223_71_T48_50216422135">852.223-71</xref>, Safety and Health, in solicitations and contracts that involve hazardous materials for the following types of requirements:
</p>
         <p outputclass="List1">(a) Research, development, or test projects.
</p>
         <p outputclass="List1">(b) Transportation of hazardous materials.
</p>
         <p outputclass="List1">(c) Construction.


</p>
